Package: IPWMethod
Type: Package
Title: Inverse Propensity Weighting Methods for Survey Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jiakun", "Lin", email = "jiak.lin@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements single and multi-reference inverse propensity weighting (IPW)
    methods, including ALP, CLW, and Raking estimators, for integrating convenience
    and probability samples with optional calibration.
